Installation
-------------

Install system dependencies:
* Requires compiler tools (gcc)
* Requires the GNU scientific library (C)

Install required R packages:
* snowfall (parallelization)
* odesolve (ordinary differential equations)
* NORMT3 (statistical distributions)
* psych (skew and kurtosis)


Compile current version from source
R CMD INSTALL warningsignals*.tar.gz


Use
---

See the examples in demo/ directory to reproduce analyses from the mansucript
